These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia, balloon-flower, orchid
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
There 4 different types of food: garlic, radish, plum, cranberry
1. the colombian is the person who growsorchid##1
2. the indonesian is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the colombian is the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person eating plum is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Flower   | dahlia    | orchid    | poppy      | balloon-flower    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Food     | cranberry  | garlic       | radish    | plum     |

