.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bus, roller, motorbike
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, tomato, broccoli, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating tomato##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person driving the roller and the person eating raspberry##2
6. the person eating carrot is between the person watching western movies and the person driving the motorbike##2
7. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Transport           | motorbike      | roller       | bus      | ship       |
| Food         | tomato    | carrot | broccoli | raspberry |

