.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
House: craftsman, ranch-style, colonial, tower
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the colonial house is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the ranch-style house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person drinking cola is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage        | tea | hot-chocolate     | cola   | coffee     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| House         | craftsman   | colonial | tower       | ranch-style    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

