.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, march, august
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
4 different games are played: domino, chess, poker, go
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the police-officer##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person playing chess##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Birthday   | august | june  | march | july       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Game         | domino | chess   | go   | poker         |

