.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, soy-milk, cola
House: art-deco, palace, cape-cod, craftsman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the palace house is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | tea         | soy-milk         | iced-tea     | cola      |
| House           | cape-cod | craftsman | art-deco    | palace     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

