4. the librarian is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the palace house is the palace house##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the craftsman house is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
9. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
