.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, peas, pear, raspberry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, lemonade, milk
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person eating pear##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person eating pear and the person drinking lemonade##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person eating pomegranate is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person eating pear is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Food   | pomegranate   | pear   | raspberry | peas |
| Beverage     | almond-milk    | milk   | tea    | lemonade  |

