.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, fuchsia, white
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, scrabble, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the person who likes green is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person who likes white is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing go and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | white        | fuchsia    | aquamarine | green   |
| Game           | go | backgammon | monopoly   | scrabble |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
| Sport         | parkour       | volleyball | cycling    | handball  |

