.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, climbing, rugby
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, bus, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | climbing    | rugby      | skiing |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Transport        | motorbike       | scooter     | bus         | boat           |

