 6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is the person playing chess##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
