7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
9. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
